reqBody.prompt: A magical girl, a guardian of light. She has long, flowing brown hair and stylized, minimalist, anime-inspired eyes that are large and expressive with simplified details, focusing on conveying emotion through shape and limited shading. She wears a flowing, magical girl outfit with a colour palette of white, gold, deep blue and dress boots. She stands with her arms outstretched to the sides, bent in her knees, palms facing downwards, knees apart, legs apart and feet apart. Reference sheet. Deep black background.
